reviewText: Govinda is so cute in this movie. He is a good actor as well as a good dancer. I have been looking for this DVD for awhile now and I finally found it here on Amazon for a good price. Worth every penny.

Govinda gives a damn good performance. Jackie is just about okay. Aishwariya is nice but Namrata steals the show from Aishwariya. Okay, she's not as good looking as her sister Shilpa but she can act.

Still worth a watch
